sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Kubernetes Gateway<br/>80/443 TCP<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Proxy as Envoy Proxy<br/>(sidecar or gateway)
    participant EPP as llm-d-router EPP<br/>ext-proc gRPC
    participant Prefill as Prefill Model Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Decode as Decode Model Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant NIXL as NIXL KV Transfer<br/>5600/TCP gRPC
    participant MC as Mooncake Client<br/>50052/TCP gRPC<br/>DaemonSet
    participant MS as Mooncake Master Store<br/>50051/TCP gRPC
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,Decode: Flow 1: Standard Inference (Gateway Mode)
        Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
        GW->>EPP: ext-proc (gRPC)<br/>Route selection
        EPP->>Decode: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
        Note over EPP: Select optimal pod<br/>(KV-cache aware, load-balanced)
        EPP-->>GW: Selected backend pod
        GW->>Decode: Forward request<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
        Decode-->>GW: Streaming response
        GW-->>Client: JSON/SSE response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,NIXL: Flow 2: P/D Disaggregated Inference
        Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions
        GW->>EPP: ext-proc route selection
        EPP->>Prefill: Forward to prefill pool<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
        Prefill->>NIXL: KV-cache transfer<br/>gRPC 5600/TCP
        NIXL->>Decode: Direct KV transfer<br/>gRPC/RDMA 5600/TCP
        EPP->>Decode: Forward to decode pool<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
        Decode-->>GW: Streaming response
        GW-->>Client: JSON/SSE response
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over Decode,MS: Flow 3: Mooncake KV-Cache Offloading
        Decode->>MC: Offload KV segments<br/>gRPC 50052/TCP
        MC->>MS: Register segments<br/>gRPC 50051/TCP
        MC->>MC: RDMA transfer to<br/>other nodes
        Note over MC: Local filesystem<br/>cache layer
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Decode,HF: Flow 4: Model Loading (Pod Startup)
        Decode->>HF: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN Bearer
        HF-->>Decode: Model artifacts
        Note over Decode: Models stored at<br/>/var/lib/llm-d/models
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,Decode: Flow 5: Standalone Mode (No Gateway)
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
        Proxy->>EPP: ext-proc (gRPC)<br/>localhost
        EPP->>Decode: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
        EPP-->>Proxy: Selected backend
        Proxy->>Decode: Forward request<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
        Decode-->>Proxy: Streaming response
        Proxy-->>Client: Response
    end
